commit d0c153bcc0567dd9ac97856563f05ba368654077
Author: Raymond Wagner <rwagner@mythtv.org>
Date:   Thu Oct 25 15:14:27 2012 -0400

    Correct handling of Artwork when database field is set to NULL.
