Date:   Fri Jul 13 17:42:47 2012 -0500

    More scheduler/recorder deadlock avoidance.
    
    RecordPending() can block so it needs to have schedLock released
    around calls to it too.
    
    (cherry picked from commit 6cb14eec6fa56ee168ef0899d375ffdaba5ee067)

commit 09d9504694eab544f993c0caa8f79872311f1d89
Author: Chris Pinkham <cpinkham@mythtv.org>
Date:   Thu Jul 12 00:53:19 2012 -0700

    Squelch an inuseprograms DB warning during HLS transcode.
    
