commit e4349138af776a7d72dc39660ab648210c0baa1f
Author: Jim Stichnoth <jstichnoth@mythtv.org>
Date:   Fri Jun 1 19:35:55 2012 -0700

    Subtitles: Only display teletext captions inside the "box" area.
    
    The spec says that characters outside the "Start Box" / "End Box"
    region should not be displayed.  Refs #10678.
    (cherry picked from commit 419fc84c5c8d25dd17e5a0fac7b6860a5f82a602)

commit bb0a48c02973462e6fe711d351f23a7e2960037a
