commit 1cbd350d57081bb5089bf97e9cc20ca267aaa899
Author: Jean-Yves Avenard <jyavenard@mythtv.org>
Date:   Fri May 25 01:10:45 2012 +1000

    Allow VDA to play interlaced content on a mac.
    
    VDA has been found to severly crash a mac when playing interlaced content. So it had been disabled.
    
    This commit allow the ability to override that behaviour with starting mythfrontend with:
    MythFrontend.app/Contents/MacOS/MythFrontend -O AllowVDAInterlace=1

